data.description: This adorable Brick Rancher in Indigo Park has been completely redone! This 3 bedroom 2 bath one level home has a bright and sunny entrance with newly built in drop area and storm door. The original ¾ Oak hardwood floors are in the living room and bedrooms. The foyer, hallway, kitchen and baths have all new LVP. All new paint. All new baseboard trim, new doors, new wood 2” blinds throughout the whole home. Updated electrical and plumbing with new outlets and fixtures. Both bathrooms have been redone. All New kitchen with new appliances, cabinets and butcher block countertops. Wood burning fireplace. One car garage. Huge back yard. $9K spent to take down trees. New landscaping. Indigo Park Pool is at the entrance of the community and you can join for a fee and they have a swim team called “The stingrays”.
